summary: Can you write something about plus size y/n being insecure about showing her body to Harry ?
question: Can you write something about plus size y/n being insecure about showing her body to Harry ?
answer:
Aww okay💖💖💖 <3 

Y/N looked at the mirror, she gained weight again.

I hate it. She thought. All I’m trying to do is lose some weight but it kept on coming back.

When Harry came home, he was fancy for a bubble bath. All he wanted his lovely girlfriend to join him, because she never showed herself to him. Harry knew that it’s because she’s insecure about her own body. But to be honest, he thinks that his girlfriend is sexy as hell.

He went upstairs, and his girlfriend was naked, looking at herself in the mirror. Harry is pretty sure that his pants was not this tight this morning. “Hey gorgeous. You look stunning like this.”

Y/N seemed shocked, she quickly put on a robe, trying to hide her body. “H…Hey, you’re back. You scared me.” She was nervous, he can tell.

She’s hiding herself from him, again.

Harry didn’t like to see her like this, he gave her a peck on her lips. “Angel, you don’t need to hide yourself from me. I love the way you are right now.”
He slide his hands up her waist, pulling her in, kissing her forehead, her cheeks, and her jaw. “And I love you.”

 She chuckled, kissing him back. “I love you too, H.”

“Now would you care to join me for a bubble bath?” Harry smiled at her.

“Of course.”

Masterlist
